"All three"? There are a lot more seasons of The OUTER LIMITS

These are the titles from the original series (1963). There was only only two series from the original show airing between 1963-1965. Series 1 E1-32, Series 2 E1-17. Series 2 (Episodes 1-17) are not in this collection and there currently seem to be no working torrents for them (that I can find). Not sure if they are still free on hulu.
